casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF David Alan VESEL.
No. D-2758.
Supreme Court of the United States
Feb. 24, 2014.
David Alan Vesel, of Creedmoor, North Carolina, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
